{
  "stem": "13213.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "In 19-- Chaim in 1944, October, 1944, and Yakov in 1947, after I already left.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I never heard of her until later on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We heard from somebody that she was in the-- she survived and she was in the-- in New York.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was in Stepan until my brother, Chaim, was killed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then, since he was the main supporter and I went to school, I continued my schooling, only went to-- in 1944, I continued into grade five.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When he was killed, I decided that I should go, maybe, and learn a trade right away.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the City Communist party, or whatever they're called-- that city there-- gave me permission to go to learn for a projectionist on movies.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I went to Lwow.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They sent me there to Lwow, and I finished there for a projectionist of movies, about six months' course.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And there, I returned-- I had to return back and to work for the government.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they gave me a helper, which we had a motor, a generator, because there was no electricity in the villages.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we had to go into the villages and show Soviet films in all the villages.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I did this for about six months, and then I figured there was no future in it.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And at the same time, the Ukrainian bandits were attacking from all over-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] every Russian or Ukrainian or Jewish people that were involved with the Soviets.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So I decided to go back to Lwow, and I went back and enrolled into a trade school.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And in the trade school, I met a friend of mine, Shlomo Grinshtain, that was also from Stepan.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we went back together there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were learning.",
      "word_count": 3
    }
  ],
